My cheap iced Americano home recipe:

- pour 20ml. boiling water in a drinking glass
- dissolve/mix 1 teaspoonful of Great Taste coffee powder in the boiling water
- add 2 ice cubes. Mix until the water turns cold
- fill up the glass with more cold water. Mix well and enjoy~
